| Item           | Recommended Format            | Example                         |
| -------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Package name   | **lowercase** (no underscore) | `halopsa`                       |
| Function names | **camelCase / PascalCase**    | `GetClient()`, `CreateTicket()` |
| Variable names | **camelCase**                 | `clientName`, `ticketStatus`    |
| Constants      | **UPPER_SNAKE_CASE**          | `API_BASE_URL`, `AUTH_TOKEN`    |
| JSON keys      | **snake_case**                | `"client_name": "ABC Corp"`     |
